    f'{base_url}/api/v4/projects/{project_id}/members/{user_id}',
    headers=headers,
    timeout=10
)

print(f"\nRemoval Status Code: {remove_response.status_code}")

if remove_response.status_code == 204:
    print("✓ Successfully removed user ID 1 (root/Administrator) from project sotopia")
elif remove_response.status_code == 200:
    print("✓ Successfully removed user ID 1 (root/Administrator) from project sotopia")
    print(f"Response: {remove_response.text}")
else:
    print(f"Response: {remove_response.text}")

# Verify the removal by checking members again
print("\nVerifying removal...")
members_response = requests.get(
    f'{base_url}/api/v4/projects/{project_id}/members/all',
    headers=headers,
    timeout=10
)

if members_response.status_code == 200:
    members = members_response.json()
    print(f"Current members after removal: {len(members)}")
    
    if len(members) == 0:
        print("✓ All project members have been successfully removed from sotopia project")
    else:
        print("Remaining members:")
        for member in members:
            print(f"  - {member.get('username')} ({member.get('name')})")
else:
    print(f"Error verifying: {members_response.text}")

print("\n" + "=" * 80)
print("Security compliance task completed.")
